<div class="content" name="NetrServerSetInfo" uuid="7adfab6e-4531-4a1f-a876-abc2ee2d8f6d"><p>The NetrServerSetInfo method sets <a href="1709f6a7-efb8-4ded-b7ae-5cee9ee36320#gt_434b0234-e970-4e8c-bdfa-e16a30d96703" data-linktype="relative-path">server</a> operating parameters
