to set and the corresponding member is listed in section <a href="fa3ad1bd-1eb9-4a32-9ca4-6d71241f4602" data-linktype="relative-path">2.2.2.12</a>.<a id="Appendix_A_Target_83"></a><a aria-label="Product behavior note 83" href="ebb74ff2-abb1-4e1b-a76a-563a5cbbea9a#Appendix_A_83" data-linktype="relative-path">&lt;83&gt;</a></p><p>The server MUST construct <a href="a8909a6f-0cef-46d1-a85b-f990cd05a739" data-linktype="relative-path">SERVER_INFO_103</a> and
SERVER_INFO_599 structures from <b>ServerConfiguration.ServerInfo103</b> and <b>ServerConfiguration.ServerInfo599</b>
